					Full Description



		Planet Communications Asia Public Company Limited is a Thailand-based provider of total solutions of telecommunication and digital television (TV) systems. The Company's business activities are divided into three categories: distribution of telecommunication products and products for digital TV, which including telecommunication system related products and broadcasting and digital TV system related products; distribution of PlanetComm products, which including telecommunication devices and controlling software as well as other general products that are designed, researched, developed, integrated, and marketed under its brand, namely PlanetComm, and services, which it offers services such as consultation, design, installation, training, repair and maintenance.
» Full Overview of PCAm.BK







