Company Description                    




                        Planet Communications Asia Public Company Limited provides development consultancy services and provides satellite communication solutions for corporate customers. The services are provided to customers in multiple technological areas such as telecommunications, PlanetComm Products,  Broadcast-Digital TV, and PlanetComm Services, which are provided  in accordance with ISO 9001:2008 quality standards. The company was incorporated in 1994 and is based in Bangkok.                     


