                                                Planet Communications Asia PCL
                                             Company Snapshot
                                            









                                            
	Planet Communications Asia PCL operates within the Electronic parts and equipment sector.
	
	In addition to historical fundamental analyses, the complete report available to purchase compares Planet Communications Asia PCL with three other
	computer and electronic stores in Asia:
		
	Taiwan Ostor Corp
	
		of Taiwan
		(2016
	sales of 666.39 million Taiwanese Dollars [US$22.06  million]
		),
	
	Trust Search Corp Ltd
	
		of Taiwan
		(641.66 million Taiwanese Dollars [US$21.24  million]
		), and
	
	Advanced Digital Chips Inc
	
		which is
		
		based in South Korea
		(25.30 billion Korean Won [US$22.59  million]
		).
	
	Sales Analysis. 
	
		During the year ended December of 2016, sales at
		Planet Communications Asia PCL were 715.46 million Thai Bahts (US$21.49 million).
	
		This
		
			is
		
			a
			
				sharp
			
			decrease of 29.8%
		
		 versus 2015, when the company's sales were 1.02 billion Thai Bahts.
	

	




 


 
 


 
 


 
 











 



 













 










