					Biographies





Name
Description




							Sanpat Sopon


					
							Mr. Sanpat Sopon serves as Chairman of the Board of Planet Communications Asia PCL. He was appointed to the Board since 2011. He holds a Master of Business Administration from Western Michigan University, USA.




							Prapat Rathlertkarn


					
							Mr. Prapat Rathlertkarn is a Vice Chairman of the Board, President and Chief Executive Officer of Planet Communications Asia PCL. He was appointed to the Board since 1994. He holds Master of Business Administration, Business Administration, Phillips University, USA.




							Trevor Thompson


					
							Mr. Trevor John Thompson serves as Vice Chairman of the Executive Board, President, Chief Technology Officer, Executive Director and Director of Planet Communications Asia PCL. He was appointed to the Board since 1994. He holds Bachelor of Commerce, Engineering, British Columbia Institute of Technology, Canada.




							Ratana Suwan


					
							Mrs. Ratana Suwan is an Executive Vice President - Finance, Executive Vice President, Director of Planet Communications Asia PCL. She was appointed to the Board since 2003. She holds a Bachelor of Accountancy from University of the Thai Chamber of Commerce. She also holds a Bachelor of Laws from Sukhothai Thammathirat Open University.




							Satit Rathlertkarn


					
							Mr. Satit Rathlertkarn is an Executive Vice President of Sales, Director of Planet Communications Asia PCL. He was appointed to the Board since 1994. He holds a Bachelor of Engineering in Electrical Engineering in Chiang Mai University, Thailand.




							Aneak Pongsabutra


					
							Mr. Aneak Pongsabutra is Vice President of Operations of Planet Communications Asia PCL. He was appointed to the Board since 1999. He holds a Master of Applied Statistics, National Institute of Development Administration (NIDA).




							Somchai Sakulwichitsintu


					
							Mr. Somchai Sakulwichitsintu Vice President of Marketing, Executive Director of Planet Communications Asia PCL. He was appointed to the Board since 1997. He holds a Master's degree in Business Economics from Kasetsart University, Thailand.




							Rungroj Jaturaworaporn


					
							Mr. Rungroj Jaturaworaporn is Vice President of Sale of Broadcast & Digital TV of Planet Communications Asia PCL since 2013. He holds a Bachelor of Electronic Engineering, King Mongkut’s Institute of Technology Ladkrabang.




							Prawich Rungdecharak


					
							Mr. Prawich Rungdecharak is Vice President of Technical Services of Planet Communications Asia PCL. He was appointed to the Board since 2000. He holds a Master of Business Administration from Mahanakorn University of Technology, Thailand.




							Wathara Arun







							Pramot Phongthong







							Somkit Wangchoetchuwong







							Katiya Greigarn


					
							Dr. Katiya Greigarn is an Independent Director of Planet Communications Asia PCL since 2011. He is also a Chairman of the Audit Committee in the Company. He holds a Bachelor of Electrical Engineering from Chulalongkorn University, a Master's degree in Electrical Engineering and a Ph.D. in Electrical Engineering from University of Missouri.




							Sompong Oui-trakul


					
							Mr. Sompong Oui-trakul is an Independent Director of Planet Communications Asia PCL since 2011. He is also a member of the Audit Committee in the Company. He holds a Master of Business Administration from Rangsit University, Thailand.




							Sutharak Soonthornpusit


					
							Mrs. Sutharak Soonthornpusit is an Independent Director of Planet Communications Asia PCL since 2011. She is also a member of the Audit Committee in the Company. She holds a Master of Science in Marketing and Economics from Ball State University, USA.











